OL,3,CMan who filmed himself setting fire to
OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FA man who filmed himself using a
OL,7,Fsecurity camera setting fire to a
OL,8,Fterraced home and then spat in the
OL,9,Fface of a police officer who rescued
OL,10,Fhim has been jailed for three years.
OL,12,FAn officer had to climb onto a fragile
OL,13,Froof and put himself at risk in order
OL,14,Fto rescue 41-year-old Martin Foley
OL,15,Ffrom the burning building on Larput
OL,16,FPlace in Cheltenham.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
