OL,3,CMan who filmed himself setting fire to
OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FFoley was seen on an internal camera
OL,7,Fwalking around inside the property on
OL,8,FLarput Place in Cheltenham on 20
OL,9,FOctober last year (2024) with a large
OL,10,Fkitchen knife.
OL,12,FGloucester Crown Court was told how
OL,13,Fthe camera footage was watched live by
OL,14,Fthe tenant of the property who was out
OL,15,Fof the country on holiday at the time.
OL,17,FHe watched as Foley took a lighter and
OL,18,Fset fire to a duvet on the bedroom
OL,19,Ffloor, which resulted in the contents
OL,20,Fof the room being destroyed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
