OL,6,FOfficers were called at 11.15am and
OL,7,Fwhen they arrived, smoke was billowing
OL,8,Fout of the address.
OL,10,FAt the time, police did not know
OL,11,Fwhether Foley was the only person
OL,12,Finside the property so they made
OL,13,Fattempts to search the premises before
OL,14,Fthe fire service arrived, but the
OL,15,Fsmoke stopped them from being able to
OL,16,Fget upstairs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
