OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FOfficers placed themselves at risk by
OL,7,Fclimbing onto a fragile roof while
OL,8,FFoley was hanging out of a rear
OL,9,Fupstairs window, and they dragged him
OL,10,Fout to safety.
OL,12,FThe court was told that Foley was
OL,13,Faggressive and had to be restrained,
OL,14,Fand during that process he spat in the
OL,15,Fface of one of the officers who was
OL,16,Fnext to him, with this landing in his
OL,17,Feye.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
