OL,6,FBodyworn video footage was played to
OL,7,Fthe court which showed the position
OL,8,FFoley was in with smoke coming out of
OL,9,Fthe window.
OL,11,FFirefighters were able to bring the
OL,12,Ffire under control with no damage
OL,13,Fcaused to neighbouring properties.
OL,15,FThe court heard how the damage caused
OL,16,Fto the property was extensive, with a
OL,17,Fsignificant refurbishment required.
