OL,6,FA statement from a co-owner of the
OL,7,Fproperty was read to the court in
OL,8,Fwhich she said: "The fire at my
OL,9,Fproperty has caused me immense stress
OL,10,Fand has been a complete shock. I am
OL,11,Fdeeply saddened to learn that this
OL,12,Fincident was deliberately caused."
OL,14,FA statement from the tenant was also
OL,15,Fread to the court in which he
OL,16,Fdescribed watching the events
OL,17,Funfolding live.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
