OL,3,CMan who filmed himself setting fire to
OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FHe said: "On 20 October, the property
OL,7,FI rented was deliberately set on fire;
OL,8,Fresulting in substantial financial
OL,9,Flosses, emotional distress, and a
OL,10,Fsignificant disruption to my daily
OL,11,Flife and sense of security. This
OL,12,Fincident has not only affected my
OL,13,Fmaterial possessions, but also my
OL,14,Fhealth and wellbeing.
OL,16,F"I watched the horror live as it
OL,17,Fhappened, leaving me feeling helpless
OL,18,Fand in distress as I saw my entire
OL,19,Flife belongings go up in flames from
OL,20,Fhundreds of miles away."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
