OL,3,CMan who filmed himself setting fire to
OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FFoley, of no fixed address, pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to arson with recklessness as
OL,8,Fto whether life was endangered,
OL,9,Fthreats to kill his then partner and
OL,10,Fassaulting an emergency worker.
OL,12,FThe court was told that Foley was
OL,13,Funder the influence of cocaine at the
OL,14,Ftime of the incident, and that he had
OL,15,Fshown remorse for his actions.
OL,16,FReferences had also been provided by
OL,17,Fprison staff which said he had been
OL,18,Fbehaving in an exemplary fashion while
OL,19,Fin prison.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
