OL,3,CMan who filmed himself setting fire to
OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FHis Honour Judge Rupert Lowe said:
OL,7,F"Police officers arrived in response
OL,8,Fto your call to find smoke billowing
OL,9,Ffrom the upstairs windows front and
OL,10,Fback, as seen on video. They evacuated
OL,11,Fthe neighbours and you were found
OL,12,Fhalfway out of an upstairs window.
OL,14,F"Officers had to help you down onto a
OL,15,Fnot very strong looking structure or
OL,16,Flean to, and when they helped you
OL,17,Fdown, of course at risk to themselves,
OL,18,Fyou were aggressive and had to be
OL,19,Frestrained and you spat in the face of
OL,20,Fthe officer."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
