OL,3,CMan who filmed himself setting fire to
OL,4,Ca flat is jailed
OL,6,FDue to the guilty pleas, Foley was
OL,7,Fgiven a 25 per cent credit on his
OL,8,Fsentence. He was sentenced to three
OL,9,Fyears in prison and was told he must
OL,10,Fserve up to half before being released
OL,11,Fon licence.
OL,13,FFollowing the sentencing,
OL,14,Finvestigating officer Detective
OL,15,FConstable Gareth Wright said: "This
OL,16,Fwas a serious incident which could
OL,17,Fhave had catastrophic consequences if
OL,18,Fthe home had become engulfed in flames.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
