OL,6,F"Thankfully officers were able to
OL,7,Fquickly evacuate the nearby properties
OL,8,Fwhile Gloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService got the fire under control.
OL,11,F"No-one should be subjected to abuse
OL,12,For physical assault at any point, let
OL,13,Falone while working, but Foley went
OL,14,Fone step further and spat in the face
OL,15,Fof one of his rescuers, which is
OL,16,Fcompletely unacceptable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
