OL,6,F"Alongside this, the ordeal was
OL,7,Fhorrible for the tenant who had to
OL,8,Fhelplessly watch live while abroad as
OL,9,Fall of his belongings caught fire, and
OL,10,Fthe incident has caused ongoing stress
OL,11,Fand upset for the home owners who are
OL,12,Fstill going through a lengthy process
OL,13,Fto try and repair the property."
